House Resolution 852
By: Representatives Adeyina of the 110th, Dawson of the 65th, and Bennett of the 94th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Dr. Ernest Ofori Sarpong; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Dr. Ernest Ofori Sarpong is widely recognized as a visionary titan of business,
3 global philanthropist extraordinaire, and trailblazing industrial pioneer whose transformative
4 entrepreneurship and bold leadership have made a great impact on Ghana and beyond; and
5 WHEREAS, rising from humble beginnings, Dr. Sarpong launched his entrepreneurial
6 journey in the 1990s with the founding of Sarpong Ventures Ltd., quickly establishing a
7 reputation for strategic brilliance and business acumen across the Central District of Accra
8 through his success in the import and trading sector; and
9 WHEREAS, he currently stands at the helm of the Special Group of Companies,
10 commanding a net worth of $600 million and serving as a beacon of determination,
11 resilience, and success in the global business landscape; and
12 WHEREAS, Dr. Sarpong's strategic leadership extends to his role as Board Chairman of Best
13 Point Savings and Loans Co. Ltd., where he has guided the institution in empowering
14 individuals and enterprises through financial inclusion and economic stability; and
